      "customOneOffs": [
        "Has 1D4x10 odor clusters; opening one or two clusters counts as one melee attack.",
        "One open cluster: 10 ft cloud; save vs non-lethal poison 16+. Failed save: gagging/nausea, -3 initiative, -1 strike/parry/dodge, -10% skills. Successful save: -1 initiative and -5% skills.",
        "Opening two clusters doubles cloud range and penalties.",
        "Odor persists 1 minute per character level and radiates with the Nightbane.",
        "Used clusters cannot be reused for 24 hours. Smashing/cutting a cluster triggers the same effect."
      ],
      "gameSystems": ["nightbane"],
